{"tid":789670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：這麼多休閒時間爽爆了，暫時不找工作 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2018-08-22T11:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T12:31:01.000Z","uid":30788,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02e1d51599b689d2047ed2fef1cc9c22f9ff7e1f","tid":789670,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"雲加在今夏世界杯期間受邀擔任貝因體育的解說嘉賓，之後就開始了悠長的假期，法國人正準備延長在科西嘉島的假期。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我決定不做決定。&rdquo;雲加接受當地報紙Corse Matin採訪時說道，&ldquo;我陶醉在這悠長的假期中，以至於讓我自己保證不會在九月前做出任何決定。（這比我想像的要好）。當你像我一樣忙碌的時候，你總會害怕突然空虛。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n雲加還透露自己最近正在閱讀菲利普-羅斯的著作《我嫁給了共產黨人》，&ldquo;我很快把自己放入了人生的這個新階段，我做了很多運動，在這裡我和朋友一起吃飯。我們交談了很多，我可以安坐幾個小時凝視地平線。我每天都在讀書，正在看菲利普-羅斯的《我嫁給了共產黨人》。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"8440cef29ad18764ea10701aa3426688d8682c81","tid":789670,"uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"搵唔到工就搵唔到工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8d28af8e527fd64b98087c406ae9569bb38951","tid":789670,"uid":144691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"g持雲爺爺回家"},{"pid":"e3d87020f105c1102f1aad6c73fbba5c1beb15b5","tid":789670,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8440cef29ad18764ea10701aa3426688d8682c81","tid":789670,"uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"搵唔到工就搵唔到工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！"},{"pid":"a506aa8a6622d7da96377d10f37550020812921c","tid":789670,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"等緊去曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a32ae210ff7e38b02a646ca8a57cf9b40934b0","tid":7896